resources.string: Hi, I am Arpit, Would you go on a date with me?

No, still no, you are chutiya

Mat maan, mai padhai karuga, guitar bajauga, drum bajauga, fachi patauga, tab aana, #thukra_ke_mera_pyaar_mera_intekaam_dekhegi
